																"TagText": {
																	"handle": "h175974c9g18dbg4459g89d2g3bafeaa2ec1c",
																	"value": "Not so for my daughter. Rion's rejoined the Flaming Fist - <i>temporarily</i>, you understand, to 'organise the craftsmen'.",
